{
  "stem": "9113.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Politch, ?] a Polack.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Then-- then we-- then we made another little place, another hiding, and we were there maybe another month, or six weeks.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] This Polack came to us at night, like maybe 12 o'clock at night.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And he came to us and he said, look.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "You have to leave this place, because we had-- we had a meeting today in church.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And our-- the-- the-- the reverend talked about you and knew exactly the location that you are, and a few fellows will come and they're gonna kill you.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "He was so good to us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "He took us to his house because we don't have nowhere to go.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "Very cold night.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "Very cold night.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "He took us to his house, and we slept over in his house.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "His wife was so good to us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "I remember I was-- I couldn't warm up myself.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "Then she took a blanket and covered us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "At night, she went down, that woman, and covered us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And in morning, we had to leave, because it was no place to be there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "We couldn't stay with him, with those people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "Because he would be killed and we would be killed.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "Then he gave us tools, because we had no more other-- the other tools was-- When they came in the same night, they bombed the whole bunker where we was.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "They-- they spoiled even that oven that we had.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "They demolished this, too.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "They-- they made everything-- nothing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "We had nothing left over.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "Then this guy prepared us another little stove.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "Took us another few days.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "He did this for us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "And we built another bunker.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "I am telling you the story so quick, but this took us days.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "It wasn't so easy to make it in a day.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
